ang \nkeyk","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5221/size6/ae9eb8bf43fd140ed624ed319d1a6382.jpg","text":"Nakakita ako ng pula at dilaw na \ninahin na nagsusulat","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5222/size6/c6b049490568ca343f31168b25652018.jpg","text":"Nakakita ako ng itim at kahel na tigre \nna nakatayo sa tubig","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5223/size6/23537cc6b6fa4a56b870d9cd6c393025.jpg","text":"Nakita ko sa aking dalawang itim na \nmata ang lahat ng kulay habang \nsila\nay lumilipad","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":194}}